items.description: "CryptoTrail" is a Python-based blockchain project that simulates the creation and validation of secure, decentralized transaction records. It generates transactions, updates account balances, and ensures block integrity through cryptographic hashing. "CryptoTrail" prevents fraudulent transactions and maintains a consistent ledger state.
